column5: Federal Fishiers fact sheet  Another good article  Hey guys, I was looking for some specific info about ideal water temp that casues Steelhead to run in numbers.  I was unable to find what  I was looking for, but thought Iwould post a few interesting articles that I came across.  Michael
Cool,  Next weekend, I hope to be 3 degrees warmer.  Also 3% less shrinkage!
